    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "高等部のみなさん、怜はいますでしょうか！\n怜！　一緒に帰りますわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ high school seniors‚ is Rei here?!\nRei! Let’s go home together!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.7,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3800,
          "startTime": 10.5
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6.7
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.266666627
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、いつも言ってるけど\n大声で私の名前を叫ばないで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ I keep telling you‚\ndon’t shout my name like that loud.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.266666627
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "こうでもしないと怜は私に気付かないでしょう？\n教室には沢山の生徒がいらっしゃる訳ですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You won’t notice me unless I do this‚ right?\nThere are so many students in the classroom.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.2000000875
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "気付くわよ！　高等部の中に中等部の制服の子が\n混じってるんだから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I would notice! A girl in a middle school uniform\nmixed in with the high school students…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.5333334605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.3666649739
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "それでは、大声はやめて差し上げます\n次からは校内放送で呼び出しますわね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ I'll kindly stop shouting.\nNext time‚ I’ll call you over the school PA system!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.7666650135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.5666649739
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "もっと却下。普通に呼びなさいよ、まったく……\n……え、妹？　違う違う、この子は同じ事務所なだけで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's even worse. Just call me normally… Seriously…\n…Eh? My little sister? No‚ no. She’s just from the same agency.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.9666650135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.9666650135
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.5666682799
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "私のことをご存じない！？\nならば教えて差し上げましょう、二代目星降る奇跡――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don’t know me?!\nThen let me introduce myself‚ the legendary \"Star-falling Miracle\" of the second generation――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.7000016529,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6766.6650138,
          "startTime": 61.4666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.0999992371
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "はいはい。私は先に帰るわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ alright. I'm going home now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.0999992371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.1666680257
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "なっ！　迎えに来たのに置いてかないでくださいまし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What?! Don’t leave me behind after I came to pick you up!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.1666680257,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12599.997242199997,
          "startTime": 75.7666652679
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vacant-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vacant-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.1666639964
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vacant-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vacant-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.1666639964
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cat-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 69.3999907176
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vacant-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vacant-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.023518389
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、猫ちゃん、楽しいかにゃー？　うりうりー\nあっ、怜ちゃんとすずにゃん！　一緒に遊ぼー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha‚ kitty‚ are you having a nyaice time? Pet‚ pet.\nAh‚ Rei-chan and Suzu-nyan! Let’s play together!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.5999986012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vacant-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vacant-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.6847299815
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "遊ぼうって、芽衣、仕事は？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Play? Mei‚ what about work?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.6847299815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vacant-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vacant-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.3180633148
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "今日はオフになったんだ。二人もオフだったよね？\n寄り道して帰ろーよ！　芽衣、パフェ食べに行きたーい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I got the day off today. You two have the day off too‚ right?\nLet’s take a detour on the way home! Mei wants to eat parfait~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.9999996185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vacant-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vacant-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.3391862473
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。構いませんわ\nそれでは、参りましょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sure. That’s fine with me.\nThen‚ shall we go?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.7725272497,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.1725272497
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.1725272497
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "放課後にカフェに寄るなんて久々かも\n何にしようかしら……どれも美味しそうで迷うわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s been a while since I stopped by a cafe after school.\nWhat should I get… Everything looks delicious‚ I can’t decide.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.2725272497,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.2725272497
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.8725205979
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "ここの猫ちゃんパフェおすすめだよ。\n猫の形のクッキーが乗ってて……芽衣これにきーめた！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I recommend the kitty parfait here.\nIt has a cat-shaped cookie on top… Mei’s decided on this!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.7333237966,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.7333237966
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.0370332322
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "可愛い……！　私もそれにしようかな\nでも、こっちのマカロンセットも捨てがたい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So cute…! Maybe I'll have that too.\nBut‚ this macaron set is tempting too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.2370414099,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.4036963385
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、次の『ミラクル☆アイドルバースデー！』\n怜でしたよね。何をするか決まっていますの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Speaking of which‚ the next 'Miracle ☆ Idol Birthday!'\nis for Rei‚ right? Have you decided what you want to do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.6037045162,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 141.8370296718
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "ミラクル……あぁ、アイドルのやりたいことを\nなんでも叶えてくれる、雑誌の誕生日企画ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Miracle… Oh‚ that birthday project in the magazine where\nthey grant any wish an idol has‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.7703711828,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 151.0703660569
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "すぐに決まったわ。テーマパークに遊びに行くつもり\nそろそろ、周年をお祝いするイベントが始まるのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I made up my mind right away. I’m going to visit a theme park.\nThey'll be starting anniversary celebration events soon.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.4370409013,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
