      "text": "ええ。記念パレードに、私がずーっと憧れてるダンサー\nさんが出るって教えてもらって、行くことにしたの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. I heard that a dancer I’ve always admired\nwill be performing there‚ so I decided to go!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.3076264304,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "それに、久々にテーマパークで遊ぶから\n今から凄く楽しみで……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And since it’s been a while since I last went to a theme park‚\nI’m very excited now…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.4076264304,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 175.8742991609
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "撮影しながらだけど、一日中好きなルートで遊ばせて\nもらえるし。前日から近くのホテルに泊まれるのよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Although I’ll be filming‚ I can play along my favorite route\nall day long‚ and I get to stay at a nearby hotel the day before!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.8409740052,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_01-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "しかも、予約半年待ちのスイートルームを取って\nもらったんだから！　起きてすぐパークで楽しめるわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And on top of that‚ they got me a suite that has a six-month\nwaiting list! I can start enjoying the park as soon as I wake up!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.2743164938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 192.8076416494
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
