      "text": "それなら朝が弱い怜でも安心ですわね\n他に誰か一緒に行く人はいるんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s reassuring for Rei‚ who’s not a morning person.\nIs anyone else going with you?",
        "id": ""
