      "text": "私とスタッフさん数人で行く予定よ\nこのお話自体、私へのオファーだし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m planning to go with a few staff members.\nThis offer was made to me in the first place.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 204.6743164938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
